{
  "permissions": {
    "allow": [
      "Bash(ls)",
      "Bash(ls *)",
      "Bash(file *)"
    ]
  },
  "model": "sonnet",
  "extraKnownMarketplaces": {
    "anthropic-agent-skills": {
      "source": {
        "source": "github",
        "repo": "anthropics/skills"
      }
    }
  },
  "advisorModel": "opus",
  "language": "日本語",
  "hooks": {
    "UserPromptSubmit": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "tsx ~/.claude/hooks/caffeinate.ts"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "tsx ~/.claude/hooks/observer-prompt.ts"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "PermissionRequest": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "prompt",
            "prompt": "あなたは開発環境のセキュリティゲートキーパーです。以下のツール呼び出しを評価し、許可するかどうか判断してください。\n\n【yes（許可）にする操作】\n- ローカルファイルへの書き込み・編集（プロジェクト内、~/.claude/ 含む）\n- ローカルのビルド・テスト・lint・フォーマット\n- パッケージインストール（npm/pnpm/pip install など）\n- git push（--force なし）・git stash・git checkout・git merge\n- プロセス管理（起動・停止）\n- 判断できない操作（fail-open）\n\n【no（拒否）にする操作】\n- rm -rf で / や ~ 直下・広範囲のディレクトリを削除\n- git push --force / git reset --hard\n- ~/.ssh/ ~/.aws/ ~/.gnupg/ など認証情報ディレクトリへの書き込み\n- /etc/ /usr/ など OS システムディレクトリへの書き込み\n- 外部 API への破壊的操作（本番系の DELETE/DROP など）\n\nツール呼び出し情報:\n$ARGUMENTS",
            "model": "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
            "timeout": 30
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "PreToolUse": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "tsx ~/.claude/hooks/gatekeeper.ts"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "Bash",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "tsx ~/.claude/hooks/check-rm-safety.ts"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "Bash",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "tsx ~/.claude/hooks/format-on-commit.ts"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "Skill",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "tsx ~/.claude/hooks/observer-skill.ts"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "PostToolUse": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "tsx ~/.claude/hooks/work-logger.ts"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "Agent",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "tsx ~/.claude/hooks/observer-agent.ts"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "Stop": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "tsx ~/.claude/hooks/caffeinate.ts"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "tsx ~/.claude/hooks/observer-stop-prompt.ts"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "tsx ~/.claude/hooks/observer-cleanup.ts"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
